<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Payment Request - {{companyName}}</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background:#f4f6f9; margin:0; padding:0; }
    .container { max-width:600px; margin:20px auto; background:#fff; border-radius:8px; padding:22px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    h1 { color:#1f8f7a; font-size:22px; margin:0 0 6px; }
    p { font-size:15px; color:#333; line-height:1.45; margin:8px 0; }
    .muted { font-size:13px; color:#777; }
    .invoice { background:#f0fbf7; border:1px solid #e6f4ef; padding:12px; border-radius:6px; margin:12px 0; }
    .amount { font-weight:700; font-size:18px; color:#0f6b57; }
    .btn { display:inline-block; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; background:#1f8f7a; color:#fff; font-weight:600; margin-top:12px; }
    .ussd { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; background:#eef8f5; padding:8px 10px; border-radius:6px; display:inline-block; margin-top:8px; }
    .footer { text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:#999; margin-top:18px; }
    .note { font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-top:10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Hi {{firstName}} ðŸ‘‹</h1>

    <p>We hope you're doing well. This is a friendly reminder that an invoice from <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> is awaiting payment.</p>

    <div class="invoice">
      <p class="muted">Invoice</p>
      <p><strong>#{{invoiceNumber}}</strong></p>
      <p class="amount">{{currency}}{{amount}}</p>
      <p class="muted">Due by: {{dueDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>To complete payment quickly on your phone, dial the USSD code below and follow the prompts:</p>

    <p class="ussd"><strong>*182*8*1*1238212*500#</strong></p>

    <p class="note">If you're on a mobile device, you can also tap the button below to open the dialer (your device will open the USSD dialer):</p>

    <!-- tel link encodes the '#' as %23 so mobile taps work -->
    <a class="btn" href="tel:*182*8*1*1238212*500%23">Pay now with USSD</a>

    <p class="note">When asked, please enter the payment reference: <strong>{{invoiceNumber}}</strong>. This helps us match your payment instantly.</p>

    <p>If you prefer another way to pay, reply to this email or contact us at <a href="mailto:{{contactEmail}}">{{contactEmail}}</a> or call <a href="tel:{{contactPhone}}">{{contactPhone}}</a>.</p>

    <p class="muted">Thanks for working with {{companyName}} â€” we appreciate you!</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{year}} {{companyName}} | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
